    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for exceptional linear power delivery. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, it sends power through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is well-sorted, featuring recent subframe reinforcement and refreshed suspension bushings to maintain its renowned handling precision. This is a mechanically sound example of BMW's finest naturally aspirated engineering, offering a visceral driving experience for the discerning purist.",
